ins. I would also like to thank the following people, without whom, none of this would have been possible, my guild The Bears of Oboo, Sabrar, Biwin, Sammeal, Chenzhan, Leolan, Annika, Corrillian, Coldlight(thanks for the mod rods), Darck, Kodylan, Nansea, Corox, Shandrel, Kaireny, Tuluvian, Lowersioux, Sirana, and especially KIRAS D'MAXAR. If I left anyone out, I'm truly sorry, I was trying to jot as many names as I could find throughout the night. It is people like these that make Lanys such a great server, and keep me playing EQ. Thanks again to everyone. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ualexxafurrytoes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alexxa Furrytoes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>w4nn4b3!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(7/22/01 6:18:46 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Kiras, my oldest and dearest friend</span><hr size=1> /UBERHUG Kiras  =) YAY YOU!!!!!!!<br>
